data.description: Welcome to this delightful single-story brick home, where comfort and style come together effortlessly. With 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a spacious open living area, this residence offers the perfect balance of functionality and charm. As you step inside, you're greeted by an inviting interior that seamlessly blends shared spaces for comfortable living. The living room flows gracefully into the open kitchen, adorned with a cozy fireplace, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. Prepare meals with joy in the well-appointed kitchen, featuring updated cabinetry, granite countertops, recessed lighting, and a stunning tiled backsplash-a chef's dream come true! Retreat to the primary bedroom, a tranquil oasis boasting an en-suite bathroom with double vanity sinks, elegant light fixtures, a walk-in shower, and a separate tub-an indulgent space for relaxation and rejuvenation. Outside, the spacious covered patio overlooks a private yard. Conveniently located just minutes from Ft Sam and Randolph AFB, this home offers both comfort and convenience in a sought-after location. Welcome to your new haven of happiness!
